1
00:00:06,980 --> 00:00:10,100
♪I love the clarity in your eyes♪

2
00:00:10,740 --> 00:00:13,860
♪Like a shooting star across my world♪

3
00:00:14,500 --> 00:00:17,580
♪Repeating the goodbye we never said♪

4
00:00:18,260 --> 00:00:21,540
♪Through sleepless nights♪

5
00:00:21,980 --> 00:00:25,100
♪I miss the way you looked at me♪

6
00:00:25,700 --> 00:00:30,260
♪Like photos freezing that summer bit by bit♪

7
00:00:30,660 --> 00:00:35,380
♪By the shore with warm winds, maybe we'll meet again♪

8
00:00:37,380 --> 00:00:41,460
[Fall in Love Again]

9
00:00:41,460 --> 00:00:43,980
[Episode 8]

10
00:00:46,040 --> 00:00:47,080
You got out of your contract?

11
00:00:49,040 --> 00:00:49,880
That's great!

12
00:00:50,040 --> 00:00:51,080
We're casting right now.

13
00:00:51,080 --> 00:00:52,000
Want to give it a shot?

14
00:00:52,320 --> 00:00:54,120
I want to join your company directly.

15
00:01:02,280 --> 00:01:04,200
Your profile is solid.

16
00:01:04,510 --> 00:01:05,480
I agree.

17
00:01:05,680 --> 00:01:06,640
What about you, Chu?

18
00:01:12,440 --> 00:01:13,600
Agree to what?

19
00:01:14,240 --> 00:01:15,360
This project just started,

20
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:16,560
and nothing's settled yet.

21
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:18,000
No, have him audition,

22
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:19,480
and see if he fits.

23
00:01:19,800 --> 00:01:20,640
I told you already.

24
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:21,800
He's got real potential.

25
00:01:21,960 --> 00:01:22,640
With what he's got,

26
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:24,200
he could jump in anytime.

27
00:01:24,440 --> 00:01:25,960
Since he's already here,

28
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:27,560
why not sign him now?

29
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:30,080
I get your point.

30
00:01:30,080 --> 00:01:31,520
Then why a trial?

31
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:32,600
Look at him.

32
00:01:32,600 --> 00:01:34,520
If you wait, someone else will take him.

33
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:36,200
I won't go anywhere.

34
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:38,480
I just want to join you.

35
00:01:38,720 --> 00:01:39,280
And

36
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:40,840
the whispers you had,

37
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,080
I heard all of it.

38
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:48,560
He's into me.

39
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:50,720
So what if he is?

40
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:52,040
Everyone appreciates beauty.

41
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:54,000
As long as it doesn't affect business.

42
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:55,480
I think

43
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,480
Yang's right.

44
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:02,240
You hear pretty well.

45
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,240
So have you decided?

46
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:06,320
Alright.

47
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:07,800
Ai.

48
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:09,400
Ai!

49
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:10,840
Draft the contract.

50
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:11,360
Okay.

51
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:16,120
As for the specific terms,

52
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:16,920
if you have any concerns...

53
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:20,400
You signed without even reading it?

54
00:02:20,640 --> 00:02:22,040
Aren't you afraid we'll sell you off?

55
00:02:22,320 --> 00:02:22,960
Not afraid.

56
00:02:24,440 --> 00:02:26,160
But please don't sell me, okay?

57
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:27,640
I want to stay with you long-term.

58
00:02:28,640 --> 00:02:30,440
What kind of talk is that?

59
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:32,200
We're a legitimate company.

60
00:02:32,600 --> 00:02:33,840
I've told you before.

61
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:36,000
Contracts need to be handled carefully.

62
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,640
No matter who you're dealing with.

63
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:38,920
No matter how close you are.

64
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:39,960
You can't just

65
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:41,480
trust people so easily, okay?

66
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:45,240
Got it.

67
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:48,800
That made him pretty happy?

68
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:50,920
Young people.

69
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:57,440
Chu.

70
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:01,080
What's going on?

71
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:06,280
We're about to set up the crew,

72
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:08,080
but our cash flow's stuck.

73
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:13,120
I'm exhausted.

74
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,320
Relax.

75
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:17,520
I wouldn't dare make you follow me

76
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:18,840
into a battle we're not ready for.

77
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:21,680
What do you mean?

78
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:25,560
This is what I saved

79
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:27,040
over ten years at Qi Siqin's company.

80
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:30,440
Enough to hold us until Mr. Wang's funds come through.

81
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,040
Chu...

82
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:35,560
Chu!

83
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:38,400
Chu, you're literally my lifesaver!

84
00:03:38,880 --> 00:03:39,880
Let me give you a kiss!

85
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,280
Get away!

86
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:43,680
Let me show my thanks with a kiss!

87
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:44,560
Don't come any closer!

88
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:55,040
Hello.

89
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:57,240
Why can't my bank card make transfers?

90
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:59,040
Haven't I already set a transfer limit?

91
00:03:59,040 --> 00:03:59,520
Hello.

92
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:00,960
Your bank card has been frozen.

93
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:03,480
What?

94
00:04:16,830 --> 00:04:18,000
Xi, what brings you here?

95
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:18,720
Where's Qi Siqin?

96
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:19,800
The director stepped out.

97
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:20,800
If you need anything, you can tell me.

98
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,440
I'll wait for him in his office.

99
00:04:21,830 --> 00:04:22,320
Xi.

100
00:04:22,660 --> 00:04:25,760
[Dream of the Mortal World]

101
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:26,560
Director, I...

102
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:31,040
Why is my bank card frozen?

103
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,720
I had no choice.

104
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:38,200
You blew this whole thing up.

105
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:39,920
My reputation's gone,

106
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:42,040
and the new project flopped too.

107
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,680
What about the money that's mine?

108
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,400
Because of what you did,

109
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:48,000
the company took serious reputational damage.

110
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,920
So we filed for bankruptcy.

111
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,040
And as for what's yours,

112
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:52,480
haven't you already taken it?

113
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:54,200
I heard you even started a new company.

114
00:04:54,520 --> 00:04:55,680
Look how successful you are.

115
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,600
And look at me.

116
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,640
Cut the crap! Don't think I don't know

117
00:04:58,640 --> 00:04:59,680
what you're really planning.

118
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,280
What am I planning?

119
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:02,800
I'm a shareholder of this company.

120
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:05,000
At least thirty percent of the funds here

121
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:05,720
belong to me!

122
00:05:05,880 --> 00:05:07,400
Then take it.

123
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:08,480
Oh wait.

124
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,440
You can't.

125
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:11,800
Because your company is bankrupt.

126
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:12,760
It doesn't exist anymore.

127
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:15,800
Qi Siqin, you're shameless!

128
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:20,800
Sit a bit longer...

129
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:43,400
Hello, Chu.

130
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:44,840
I've been calling you so many times

131
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:45,600
but you didn't pick up.

132
00:05:45,960 --> 00:05:46,760
Are you okay?

133
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:47,800
Yang,

134
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,480
I'm sorry.

135
00:05:50,280 --> 00:05:51,960
I messed everything up.

136
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:07,920
Yang,

137
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,600
do you think Mr. Wang will agree?

138
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,240
We've put in so much work.

139
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,680
Mr. Wang has seen all of it.

140
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,040
He'll understand.

141
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,000
I don't understand!

142
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,200
And I don't want to.

143
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:18,600
Since the contract is signed,

144
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:20,040
you should honor it.

145
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:21,440
Nothing else matters.

146
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:23,000
Mr. Wang, I know you're angry,

147
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,800
but we came in good faith.

148
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:26,400
Could you give us a chance to explain?

149
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:27,800
I don't want explanations.

150
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:28,680
I don't want to hear them.

151
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:31,880
Don't use your street tricks on me.

152
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:34,760
My company runs on clear rules.

153
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:35,520
Mr. Wang,

154
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:38,160
our early funding chain collapsed.

155
00:06:38,400 --> 00:06:39,520
We couldn't meet your terms.

156
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:40,360
I'm sorry.

157
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,520
How about this?

158
00:06:43,760 --> 00:06:45,960
We can renegotiate the profit split.

159
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:47,560
Your funding's already broken

160
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,760
and you're talking profit?

161
00:06:49,520 --> 00:06:50,320
Trying to play me?

162
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:51,800
But we've been working on this for so long,

163
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:53,720
and we haven't received your first payment.

164
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:55,080
I'll say it again.

165
00:06:55,080 --> 00:06:56,720
I act by the contract.

166
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:59,240
If you knew you couldn't do it,

167
00:06:59,280 --> 00:07:00,240
why did you sign?

168
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:01,840
Your terms were that strict.

169
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:03,280
How could we possibly meet them?

170
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:04,480
Can't do it, right?

171
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:05,400
Then pay what you owe

172
00:07:05,520 --> 00:07:06,360
and go your separate ways!

173
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,440
This time,

174
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:17,440
I let everyone down and wasted your trust and effort.

175
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:20,040
Everyone already gave it their all.

176
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:21,320
No one let anyone down.

177
00:07:21,840 --> 00:07:23,240
No one could've predicted

178
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:24,240
something like this.

179
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:25,480
The road is long,

180
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,480
but there's still a long future ahead.

181
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:27,840
Ms. Chu, don't lose heart.

182
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:28,600
Yeah.

183
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:30,680
Ms. Chu and Ms. Yang's abilities and character.

184
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,800
We've all seen it.

185
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:33,960
We're willing to get through this together.

186
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:34,920
- Yeah. - Yeah.

187
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:35,120
- Exactly. - Exactly.

188
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,160
- Together. - Together.

189
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:38,160
Thank you all for believing in us.

190
00:07:39,520 --> 00:07:40,640
If anyone wants to leave,

191
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:42,080
we won't stop you.

192
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:44,320
But if you're willing to stay,

193
00:07:45,160 --> 00:07:47,080
Chu and I will run this company right.

194
00:07:47,640 --> 00:07:49,240
We won't let you down.

195
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:50,400
Thank you, everyone.

196
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,120
- Thanks. - Thanks.

197
00:07:52,160 --> 00:07:52,600
- Let's drink. - Let's drink.

198
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,600
- Cheers. - Let's toast.

199
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,720
But I still owe you two an apology.

200
00:08:00,080 --> 00:08:02,320
You just signed on and the project got paused.

201
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:03,480
I'm really sorry.

202
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:05,320
I'm willing to stand with the company.

203
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:06,880
Me too.

204
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:10,160
Thank you.

205
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:13,120
- Come on, let's all have another toast. - Drink.

206
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:13,840
- Okay. - Okay.

207
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:18,360
- Cheers. - Cheers.

208
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:19,520
- Stay strong. - We can do this.

209
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:20,800
No worries.

210
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:21,720
- We'll get through this. - Let's not stand on ceremony.

211
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,520
Don't be so formal.

212
00:08:22,880 --> 00:08:23,680
Exactly.

213
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,200
Why are you here?

214
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,440
Are you okay?

215
00:08:37,150 --> 00:08:37,840
I was worried about you.

216
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:47,520
Careful.

217
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,360
Take me home.

218
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:53,600
Okay.

219
00:08:56,660 --> 00:08:57,740
[Please conserve water]

220
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:15,800
What's my door code?

221
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:19,080
How would I know your door code?

222
00:09:20,280 --> 00:09:21,080
Oh right.

223
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:25,520
Careful.

224
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:28,240
Tell me the code, I'll open it.

225
00:09:36,920 --> 00:09:41,000
My door code is...

226
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:49,080
You...

227
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:53,080
Remember it.

228
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:57,960
♪When clouds sink into the deep sea♪

229
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:58,960
Stand still.

230
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:01,240
♪Ripples spread♪

231
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:04,320
♪Traces of a racing heart♪

232
00:10:05,160 --> 00:10:07,800
♪Is it the sky or its reflection♪

233
00:10:08,060 --> 00:10:09,020
Welcome home.

234
00:10:09,020 --> 00:10:11,280
♪I can't tell anymore♪

235
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:15,600
♪Lost in your eyes♪

236
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:19,800
Ms. Chu.

237
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:22,720
Are you okay?

238
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:24,280
♪The space of an embrace♪

239
00:10:24,880 --> 00:10:27,480
♪Scatters the dark♪

240
00:10:28,160 --> 00:10:31,760
♪When the wind comes, raise the sails♪

241
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:34,040
♪And sail on...♪

242
00:10:36,160 --> 00:10:36,720
I'm sorry.

243
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:43,880
You pushed me away.

244
00:10:44,760 --> 00:10:45,560
What's wrong?

245
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,120
Am I that bad?

246
00:10:48,040 --> 00:10:49,280
Do you know what you're doing?

247
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:51,680
Who am I?

248
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:53,240
He Zheng.

249
00:10:58,560 --> 00:11:02,880
♪Trusting we'll reach a warm shore♪

250
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:08,640
♪Where even migratory birds can't reach, you're by my side♪

251
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:09,440
[Opening Week Results]

252
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:15,120
♪I'll break through the haze and run toward what I once longed for♪

253
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:20,160
♪Even if I'm hurt, I won't wander alone♪

254
00:11:21,760 --> 00:11:24,560
♪You're where my heart belongs♪

255
00:11:41,920 --> 00:11:44,000
Chu Jingxi!

256
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:46,120
How did you lose control like that?

257
00:11:59,560 --> 00:12:00,880
Never thought one day

258
00:12:00,880 --> 00:12:02,520
I'd open my own front door like a blind box.

259
00:12:11,280 --> 00:12:12,080
He Zheng.

260
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:18,280
He Zheng?

261
00:12:24,760 --> 00:12:25,240
You're awake.

262
00:12:26,800 --> 00:12:27,760
Why are you still here?

263
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:31,360
I made you breakfast.

264
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:32,080
[Delivery]

265
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:32,680
Eat it while it's hot.

266
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:33,600
Thanks for the thought.

267
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:34,280
I'm not eating.

268
00:12:34,280 --> 00:12:35,640
Please leave now.

269
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:41,960
You...

270
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:44,480
You didn't forget last night, did you?

271
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:45,560
Last night we both...

272
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:48,000
Had too much to drink.

273
00:12:51,280 --> 00:12:52,000
I wasn't drunk.

274
00:12:52,920 --> 00:12:54,960
Don't be so impulsive, kid.

275
00:12:55,920 --> 00:12:57,960
Last night was just a drunken mistake.

276
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:08,960
I like you.

277
00:13:10,280 --> 00:13:11,120
Be my girlfriend.

278
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:16,680
Okay.

279
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:18,920
What did you say?

280
00:13:19,880 --> 00:13:21,640
I said okay.

281
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:51,160
♪When clouds sink into the deep sea♪

282
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:54,440
♪Ripples spread♪

283
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:57,520
♪Traces of a racing heart♪

284
00:13:58,360 --> 00:14:01,000
♪Is it the sky or its reflection♪

285
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:04,480
♪I can't tell anymore♪

286
00:14:05,520 --> 00:14:08,800
♪Lost in your eyes♪

287
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:14,320
♪As we draw closer♪

288
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:17,480
♪The space of an embrace♪

289
